OL,5,Cmessages
OL,7,FThose messages referred to women as
OL,8,F"lazy cow(s)", "f****** bint(s)" (a
OL,9,Fderogatory term for women) and
OL,10,Fdiscussed wanting to harm a senior
OL,11,Fwoman within the service.
OL,13,FIn one message, Mr Hardiman said:
OL,14,F"I've calmed down now but I could
OL,15,Fstill kill her buddy".
OL,17,FJan Morris, who felt forced to leave
OL,18,Fher job, told ITV News that the
OL,19,Fcomments had destroyed her career.
