OL,7,FFollowing a five-month investigation,
OL,8,Fduring which both men have been on
OL,9,Fleave with stress, it was announced
OL,10,Ftoday that Mr Hardiman had been
OL,11,Fallowed to return to his job.
OL,13,FHe has been given a written warning
OL,14,Fand will have to undergo mandatory
OL,15,Ftraining.
