OL,7,FResponding to the outcome of the
OL,8,Finvestigation, Mr Hardiman said in a
OL,9,Fstatement: "I recognise this has been
OL,10,Fan unsettling time for the Service and
OL,11,FI want to apologise for the upset that
OL,12,Fhas been caused.
OL,14,F"Whilst I am confident that what has
OL,15,Fbeen reported publicly doesn't
OL,16,Frepresent me as an individual or the
OL,17,FService I am so proud to lead, I do of
OL,18,Fcourse recognise there are lessons to
OL,19,Fbe learned.
