OL,7,F"I am looking forward to getting back
OL,8,Fto doing the job I love and to working
OL,9,Falongside such a great team at
OL,10,FShropshire Fire and Rescue."
OL,12,FHowever, several women within the fire
OL,13,Fsector have expressed their outrage to
OL,14,FITV News at what they perceive to be
OL,15,Flenient action.
OL,17,FMs Morris said she felt her complaints
OL,18,Fhad been minimised and noted that she
OL,19,Fhas not received a personal apology
OL,20,Ffrom Mr Hardiman.
