OL,7,FITV News has investigated multiple
OL,8,Ffire services over the past two years,
OL,9,Frepeatedly uncovering claims of sexual
OL,10,Fharassment, misogyny and bullying.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FTwo chief fire officers have retired
OL,18,Ffollowing damning reviews of their
OL,19,Fservices, sparked by ITV News'
OL,20,Freporting. However, both are entitled
OL,21,Fto a full pension.
