OL,7,FNo chief fire officer has yet received
OL,8,Fa serious sanction, despite a
OL,9,Fparliamentary inquiry concluding this
OL,10,Fyear that the fire sector is
OL,11,F"institutionally racist, misogynist
OL,12,Fand homophobic".
OL,14,FThe investigation into ACFO Adam
OL,15,FMatthews continues.
